.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-5::.
There 2 different types of food: lime, raspberry
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, vegafina
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |
| Food        | lime      | raspberry  |
| Cigar       | vegafina     | prince    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | skateboard |

